author: Xbox
description:
EBOLA VILLAGE is a classic horror inspired by 90s survival games, presented as a modern first-person experience. After a disturbing report about a biological threat, Maria travels to a remote village to visit her family—only to face a living nightmare.

Uncover the village’s dark past and immerse yourself in a tense, oppressive atmosphere where fear lurks at every step.

Pre-orders are now available: https://www.microsoft.com/store/productid/9n6wqfsk8r3x
